<Legal title="Terms of Use" updated="June 2026">
  <p>
    These Terms govern your use of the PinSeeker iPhone app. By using PinSeeker you
    agree to them. <strong>This is a starting draft in plain language — please have it
    reviewed before relying on it.</strong>
  </p>

  <h2>Licence</h2>
  <p>
    We grant you a personal, non-transferable licence to use PinSeeker on your own
    devices for your own putting practice, subject to these Terms and the App Store
    terms.
  </p>

  <h2>Free and Pro plans</h2>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Free:</strong> {site.freeDailyPutts} measured putts per day, with full features, at no cost and with no payment details required.</li>
    <li><strong>Pro:</strong> unlimited putts for {site.pricePerMonth}/month or {site.pricePerYear}/year.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Subscriptions</h2>
  <p>
    Pro subscriptions are billed through your Apple ID and renew automatically unless
    cancelled at least 24 hours before the end of the current period. You can manage or
    cancel a subscription anytime in your App Store account settings. Refunds are
    handled by Apple under its policies.
  </p>

  <h2>It's a training aid</h2>
  <p>
    PinSeeker provides estimated measurements and coaching to help you practise. The
    numbers are computed from camera data and are intended for training, not as
    certified instrument readings. Results depend on your setup, lighting and equipment.
  </p>

