    PinSeeker is provided "as is", without warranties of any kind. To the maximum extent
    permitted by law, we are not liable for indirect or incidental damages arising from
    your use of the app.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update these Terms as the app evolves; continued use means you accept the updated Terms.</p>

  <h2>Contact</h2>
  <p>Questions? Email <a href={`mailto:${site.supportEmail}`}>{site.supportEmail}</a>.</p>
</Legal>
